<<Reverse GeoCoding>>
Step 1: Declare and initialize the object of GeoCoder

Step 2: Perform the reverseGeoCoding:
        *reverseGeoCoding: Converting lat,lng to actual physical address

Step 3: use the method getFromLocation(latitude,longitude,1) with the object of
        GeoCoder class to get the List of Address
Step 4: Get the address, town, city, postal code and country information
        related to particular latitude, longitude.


<<Sending Message>>
Step 1: Declare and initialize the object of SMS Manager class
        call the method sendTextMessage to send the message.